lead_paragraph: Five Czechs who had been missing and presumed kidnapped in Lebanon last year came home on Thursday after the Czech government freed two Lebanese citizens who were wanted by the United States.

headline.print_headline: Czech Republic: Detainees Return Home From Lebanon
